"The plugin to <link linkend=\"measure-distances\">measure distances between "
"two or more points</link>."
msgstr ""
"O 'plugin' para <link linkend=\"measure-distances\">medir as distâncias "
"entre dois ou mais pontos</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
